  <name>Samtal</name>
  <summary>A Material Design based Internet Relay Chat client</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A simple Internet Relay Chat (IRC) client that is designed to integrate
      seamlessly with the Liri OS and apps, but can also be used on other
      platforms as well.
    </p>
    <p>
      It features a simple and clean user interface, which allows you to
      focus on your conversations.
    </p>
    <p>
      Samtal allows you to publicly chat with people in a channel, and to
      have private one-to-one conversations.
    </p>
  </description>
